{"tid":718031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係條街比耶撚傳道","createTime":"2018-06-26T13:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T14:53:55.000Z","uid":125794,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"caa11cf923cd965c24346cd9c1d2ae22454f123e","tid":718031,"uid":125794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"我話唔撚信  信唔信耶穌我都係咁生活<br />\n佢話信左唔會突然變好  但睇事物既角度唔同左  好似陽光咁照落黎所有野都清晰美麗<br />\n<br />\n我沖沖下涼突然發覺佢講得好岩<br />\n件事既本質唔會變  睇你點對待佢<br />\n<br />\n我發現<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屎就係屎!</span><br />\n陽光照落黎就係更加嘔心  仲聞到有啲臭既屎!<br />\n<br />\n我明白點解咁多青年人自殺<br />\n因為生存真係好撚難<br />\n自問生活比上不足  比下有餘<br />\n但人生既壓力真係無窮無盡<br />\n究竟幾時先挨到老?"},{"pid":"ba316d18be1490f5ce46602b2a46d52c9d515003","tid":718031,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8617a54bcdc930f3c7c47954bb9f8e21954ffd","tid":718031,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}